    "Available placeholders: `{EAN}` (falls back to `{REF}` when the reference has no EAN), `{REF}` (catalog reference), `{INC}` (1-based capture counter, seeded from today's GS production so a re-capture on a different day starts back at 1). Always end with `.jpg`. Patterns that resolve to the same filename family share the counter — uploads never overwrite each other.": {
